      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Professor Petra Wend (Principal &amp; Vice-Chancellor of QMU) and Dr Richard Butt (Deputy Principal of QMU) have officiated in this summer’s overseas graduation ceremonies at the University’s partner institutions in India and Greece.</p>
<p class="txtMainBlack">QMU operates a number of teaching partnerships with organisations in Scotland, across the UK and around the world. Through these partnerships, students can study for QMU qualifications in a manner and at a location most convenient to them.</p>]]></Value>
